OL,3,CGovernment target to cut crown court
OL,4,Cbacklogs 'no longer achievable' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe Government's target of cutting the
OL,8,Fcrown court backlog is "no longer
OL,9,Fachievable", Whitehall's spending
OL,10,Fwatchdog has found.
OL,12,FA report by the National Audit Office
OL,13,F(NAO) said the Ministry of Justice aim
OL,14,Fto reduce the outstanding caseload to
OL,15,F53,000 by March 2025 was not likely to
OL,16,Fbe reached.
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@KO]
