OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FMore than a quarter of cases are
OL,8,Fwaiting for a year or more to be
OL,9,Fheard, "prolonging the distress to
OL,10,Fvictims" waiting for justice,
OL,11,Faccording to the findings.
OL,13,FAnd there have been reports of some
OL,14,Ftrials due to take place this week
OL,15,Fbeing adjourned until 2026.
