OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FOvercrowding in prisons is now "one of
OL,8,Fthe biggest obstacles" to cutting the
OL,9,Fbacklog and the MoJ is unable to say
OL,10,Fhow much money it has spent on efforts
OL,11,Fto reduce the waiting list of cases,
OL,12,Fthe NAO said.
OL,14,FThe department set the target during a
OL,15,Fspending review in October 2021 after
OL,16,Fbeing given #477 million to "support
OL,17,Frecovery across the criminal justice
OL,18,Fsystem", including reducing caseloads.
OL,19,FBut the backlog is now higher than it
OL,20,Fwas then and the MoJ estimates it will
OL,21,Fbe closer to 64,000 by March 2025.
