OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThere were 67,492 outstanding crown
OL,8,Fcourt cases as of March this year,
OL,9,Fcompared to 60,191 in March last year,
OL,10,Fprovisional MoJ figures published
OL,11,Fearlier this month suggested.
OL,13,FThe condition of the crown court
OL,14,Fbuildings could also become a
OL,15,F"barrier" to reducing the backlog
OL,16,Fbecause they are not fit for purpose
OL,17,Fdue to long-term under-investment.
