OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FCourtrooms are frequently taken out of
OL,8,Faction due to problems like leaks or
OL,9,Fheating failures. In 2022, the MoJ
OL,10,Festimated that 50% of crown court
OL,11,Fcourtrooms were at risk of sudden
OL,12,Fclosure at any time, according to the
OL,13,Ffindings.
OL,15,FThe justice system has been the
OL,16,Fsubject of increasingly febrile
OL,17,Fpolitical debate in recent years and
OL,18,Fthis may ramp up during the General
OL,19,FElection campaign.
