OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe Government is yet to honour its
OL,8,F2019 manifesto pledge of carrying out
OL,9,Fa root-and-branch review of the
OL,10,Fcriminal justice system.
OL,12,FThe royal commission pledged to carry
OL,13,Fout a "fundamental review" in a bid to
OL,14,Fimprove "efficiency and effectiveness".
OL,16,FEven though it would have been the
OL,17,Ffirst inquiry of its kind launched
OL,18,Fsince 1991, the scope and duration of
OL,19,Fthe probe, as well as the names of the
OL,20,Ffigures who would lead it, were never
OL,21,Fset out by the MoJ.
