OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FTana Adkin KC, chairwoman of the
OL,8,FCriminal Bar Association, said the NAO
OL,9,Freport "confirms" what lawyers have
OL,10,Fknown for years, "that the criminal
OL,11,Fjustice system remains in crisis
OL,12,Fwithout a plan for sustained
OL,13,Finvestment, despite the repeated
OL,14,Fwarnings of prosecutors and defence
OL,15,Fadvocates who are tasked with
OL,16,Fdelivering justice daily in our
OL,17,Fpublicly funded courts".
