OL,7,FThe Law Society of England and Wales,
OL,8,Fwhich represents solicitors,
OL,9,Freiterated calls for "urgent"
OL,10,Fimprovements to be made in light of
OL,11,Fthe findings.
OL,13,FThe body's president Nick Emmerson
OL,14,Fsaid: "The UK government's short
OL,15,Fsighted approach to justice including
OL,16,Fmore than a decade of underfunding of
OL,17,Four criminal justice system, has
OL,18,Fresulted in a chronic shortage of
OL,19,Fjudges and lawyers, huge backlogs,
OL,20,Fcrumbling courts and prison spaces
OL,21,Frunning out.
OL,26,@qD@VOUqD@]O]vD@GOU
