OL,7,F"Urgent action is needed, including
OL,8,Fsustained investment across the
OL,9,Fcriminal justice system, to ensure
OL,10,Ftimely justice for all. If the
OL,11,FGovernment had listened to our
OL,12,Fwarnings sooner, it would not have
OL,13,Ffound itself in the critical state we
OL,14,Fnow see with emergency measures being
OL,15,Ftaken to deal with the crisis over
OL,16,Fprison spaces."
OL,18,FA Ministry of Justice spokesman said
OL,19,Fcrown courts sat for more than 107,000
OL,20,Fdays last year ` "more days than at
OL,21,Fany point in the last seven years".
