OL,7,FThe Government is also "investing more
OL,8,Fin the system, rolling out remote
OL,9,Fhearings, extending the use of
OL,10,FNightingale courts and recruiting
OL,11,Fhundreds of judges to get victims the
OL,12,Fjustice they deserve and put more
OL,13,Foffenders behind bars" as well as
OL,14,F"pushing ahead with the largest prison
OL,15,Fexpansion programme in 100 years `
OL,16,Fwith 10,000 of the 20,000 additional
OL,17,Fplaces to be delivered by the end of
OL,18,F2025", he added.
